Feature: Lumos

    Creates a narrow beam of light that shines from the wand's tip, like a
    torch (US: flashlight).

    Pronunciation:
        /ˈljuːmɒs/ LEW-mos
    Seen/mentioned:
        First seen in Chamber of Secrets and then constantly throughout the
        series.
    Suggested etymology: - 
    Notes:
        The counter spell, Nox, extinguishes the light. The caster of this
        spell can cast other spells while this spell is in effect.